OL,4,Cdamage after Paddington Bear statue
OL,5,Ccut in half
OL,7,FThe actions of two Royal Air Force
OL,8,Fengineers who broke a newly-installed
OL,9,FPaddington Bear statue in half before
OL,10,Fstealing it were "the antithesis of
OL,11,Feverything Paddington stands for", a
OL,12,Fjudge said.
OL,14,FDaniel Heath and William Lawrence, who
OL,15,Fare both 22 and work as engineers at
OL,16,FRAF Odiham in Hampshire, had been
OL,17,Fdrinking when they damaged the statue
OL,18,Fat 2am on March 2, after a night out.
