OL,7,FCCTV footage played to Reading
OL,8,FMagistrates' Court showed them
OL,9,Fapproaching the Paddington Bear
OL,10,Fstatute on Northbrook Street before
OL,11,Fteaming up in an attempt to rip the
OL,12,Fbear off the bench.
