OL,7,FThe pair were ordered to pay #2,725
OL,8,Feach towards the costs of repairing
OL,9,Fthe statue.
OL,11,FThey have also been sentenced to a 12-
OL,12,Fmonth community order and ordered to
OL,13,Fcarry out 150 hours of unpaid work "as
OL,14,Fpayback to the community for your
OL,15,Factions", the judge said.
